            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#DEE">
                <p>To [...]ius Innocens. [...] dies from the will of him (that his) bones are in a vaulted room (?) [...] their statues [...] and a seated statue of him has been allowed [...] mother at her own expense.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it" resp="#DEE">
                <p>Per [...]ius Innocens. [...] muore dal testamento di lui (che le sue) ossa siano in una stanza ad arco (?) [...] le sue statue [...] e una statua seduta di lui è stata concessa [...] madre a sue spesse.</p>
            </div>
